data.description: PRICE REDUCED! Great restored historic commercial property in Belle Fourche. Originally built as a VFW with a meeting hall upstairs and a bar downstairs, this all metal building has great charm and recent upgrades. All new electric service, entry way flooring, doors, deck, gutters, in 2014. New plumbing fixtures included just need to be hooked up. Off street parking, CoRayVac radiant heating upstairs, new track lighting system throughout the showroom, 10'x10' main floor office and a new heavy timber 16'x12' deck on the front of building. Low taxes and a great price to own your own piece of commercial property. Call Mike at (605)645-3472 or Tim at (605)580-0252.
